Church, G. M., Gao, Y. & Kosuri, S. Next-generation digital information storage in DNA. Science 337, 1628, doi:10.1126/science.1226355 (2012).
Moe-şBehrens, G. H. The biological microprocessor, or how to build a computer with biological parts. Computational and Structural Biotechnology Journal 7 (2013).
Pease, R. How to turn living cells into computers. Nature News & Comment, doi:doi:10.1038/nature.2013.12406 (2013).
Salis, H. M., Mirsky, E. A. & Voigt, C. A. Automated design of synthetic ribosome binding sites to control protein expression. Nat Biotechnol 27, 946-950, doi:10.1038/nbt.1568 (2009).
Chen, Y. J. et al. Characterization of 582 natural and synthetic terminators and quantification of their design constraints. Nature methods 10, 659-664, doi:10.1038/nmeth.2515 (2013).
Mutalik, V. K. et al. Precise and reliable gene expression via standard transcription and translation initiation elements. Nature methods 10, 354-360, doi:10.1038/nmeth.2404 (2013).
Mutalik, V. K. et al. Quantitative estimation of activity and quality for collections of functional genetic elements. Nature methods 10, 347-353, doi:10.1038/nmeth.2403 (2013).
Chappell, J., Jensen, K. & Freemont, P. S. Validation of an entirely in vitro approach for rapid prototyping of DNA regulatory elements for synthetic biology. Nucleic Acids Res 41, 3471-3481, doi:10.1093/nar/gkt052 (2013).

撰稿｜楊志賢
編輯｜吳子青、餘玟萱
